Package: DEExplorer
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Exploration of Bulk RNA-seq Differential Expression Results
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("DEExplorer", "Team", email = "team@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package-oriented Shiny components to explore edgeR DGEList
    objects together with limma differential expression fits produced by
    eBayes() or treat(). Includes PCA/QC views, linked MA and volcano
    exploration, contrast-aware DEG tables, and lasso-driven Enrichr workflows.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
    bslib,
    DT,
    edgeR,
    httr2,
    limma,
    plotly,
    shiny
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Author: DEExplorer Team [aut, cre]
Maintainer: DEExplorer Team <team@example.com>
